text: Jorge Molina Valdivieso (born 16 February 1932) is a Chilean politician who served as President of the Chamber of Deputies and as a member of the Chamber of Deputies, representing District 12 of the Valparaíso Region. ==References== Category:1932 births Category:Living people Category:Presidents of the Chamber of Deputies of Chile Category:Party for Democracy (Chile) politicians Category:Pontifical Catholic University of Valparaíso alumni
title: Jorge Molina Valdivieso
